### Suggestions for a candidate
- [ ] Study advanced PHP features such as `array_pad`, `array_all`, `match` and others to stay updated with the latest language improvements.
    - [X] Theory
        - array_pad creates more indexes on a array in order for it to have the given size. The value of the new indexes can be specified too
        - array_all test all the array data in order to understand of all of the itens match the operation coded into a given callback
        - match is like switch but has a diferent sintax
    - [ ] Pratice some
- [ ] Deepen knowledge of design patterns beyond MVC, such as Factory, Singleton, and Strategy, to enhance system design skills.
    - [ ] Theory
    - [ ] Pratice some
- [ ] Gain hands-on experience with NoSQL databases like MongoDB to broaden database management skills.
    - [ ] Theory
    - [ ] Pratice some
- [ ] Familiarize yourself with HTTP methods like PATCH and their best practices to enhance API development skills.
